&lt;li data-start=&quot;1135&quot; data-end=&quot;1203&quot;&gt;Experience working with website platforms like WordPress and Duda.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1206&quot; data-end=&quot;1270&quot;&gt;Basic understanding of HTML and CSS from a design perspective.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1273&quot; data-end=&quot;1332&quot;&gt;Strong problem-solving abilities and attention to detail.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1335&quot; data-end=&quot;1413&quot;&gt;Ability to collaborate effectively in a fast-paced, remote team environment.&lt;/li&gt;
